{
  "text": "The colony-forming ability of MM-4 cells in semisolid agar was estimated in 0.33 % agar (\u00abDifco\u00bb, USA) in DMEM plus 10 % NCS in vitro [CITATION_1] . The plates were incubated for 14 days in a humid atmosphere at 37 o C in the presence of 5 % CO 2 , then the number and the size of colonies were determined in each well using binocular magnifier BM-51-2 (\u00abLOMO\u00bb). The size of colony was defined as small (10-20 cells), middle (21-50 cells) and large (more than 50 cells) [CITATION_2] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
